      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those who value utility over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches, a few minor dings, and some paint fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and there are some stains on the carpet, but all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a solid, dependable driver for anyone needing a budget-friendly commute.",
