    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 951-spec Porsche 944 Turbo. Powered by the intercooled M44/51 2.5L inline-four, this unit features factory-forged internals and a responsive KKK K26 turbocharger. The rear-mounted 5-speed transaxle ensures a near-perfect 50/50 weight distribution, providing exceptional balance and turn-in precision. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt and water pump service, along with a vacuum system refresh to maintain consistent boost levels. The braking system utilizes four-piston Brembo calipers for significant thermal management. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are optimized for immediate performance use.",
